# Wrapper4AI

**Multi-provider, pluggable LLM wrapper with token counting, history management, and seamless extensibility.**

> ğŸ”§ Designed for developers building chat-based AI tools with OpenAI, Gemini, Bedrock, DeepSeek, Anthropic, and more.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- ğŸ”Œ **Unified interface** for multiple LLM providers
- ğŸ’¬ **Chat history tracking** with token trimming
- ğŸ”¢ **Token counting** with Tiktoken for OpenAI models
- ğŸ“š **Extensible handler base** for adding new models
- âœ… **Testable client API** with clean abstraction

